6: All right, I guess that's about good.
8:
Now to just toss in some soy sauce, 
and it'll be ready to serve.
18:
I heard from Light that you could use 
some help.
20:
I know my way around a kitchen; 
might I lend you a hand?
24:
If you don't mind, that'd be amazing! 
Thank you, Shirano.
32:
Goodness, you certainly keep the 
place well-stocked. Bless your heart, 
there's even soy sauce.

I've been using it for almost everyth—

it?

assumed that's how it's supposed to

mouths to feed! I suppose we haven't

76:
Now, listen here, young man! The art

rise and fall with the tides of time. 
Do you understand?
85:
Good. Meet me here tomorrow 
evening.
87:
I'll give you a taste of TRUE Yamato 
cuisine!
94:
Shirano, you prepared all of this 
yourself?! I-I could never make

97:
The attention to detail is superb.

king back in my world.

full potentials!

There's nothing wrong with strong

such an avid learner!
143:
Ah, if only the princess would put half 
so much energy into her studies!
149:
Shirano! Please teach me more about 
cooking!

156:

161: Thank you! I'll do my best to—
